msgctxt "56"
msgid "How to Play Hidden Cricket:"
msgstr "How to Play Hidden Cricket:"

msgctxt "68"
msgid "Unlike standard cricket, hidden cricket uses seven hidden numbers."
msgstr "Unlike standard cricket, hidden cricket uses seven hidden numbers."

msgctxt "80"
msgid ""
"The seven numbers are hidden at the start of the game, and are not revealed "
"until they are hit by a player."
msgstr ""
"The seven numbers are hidden at the start of the game, and are not revealed "
"until they are hit by a player."

msgctxt "92"
msgid ""
"Players who reveal a hidden number by hitting it for the first time receive "
"an open bonus."
msgstr ""
"Players who reveal a hidden number by hitting it for the first time receive "
"an open bonus."

msgctxt "104"
msgid ""
"Hitting numbers in the single ring counts as one hit, the double ring as two"
" hits, and the triple ring as three hits."
msgstr ""
"Hitting numbers in the single ring counts as one hit, the double ring as two"
" hits, and the triple ring as three hits."

msgctxt "116"
msgid "Three hits on a number closes it."
msgstr "Three hits on a number closes it."

msgctxt "128"
msgid ""
"The points from subsequent hits on a number you closed are added to your "
"score."
msgstr ""
"The points from subsequent hits on a number you closed are added to your "
"score."

msgctxt "140"
msgid ""
"However, if your opponent closes that number as well, you will no longer get"
" points when you hit it."
msgstr ""
"However, if your opponent closes that number as well, you will no longer get"
" points when you hit it."

msgctxt "152"
msgid ""
"The player with the highest score at the end of the allotted number of "
"rounds wins."
msgstr ""
"The player with the highest score at the end of the allotted number of "
"rounds wins."

msgctxt "164"
msgid ""
"You can also win if you close all the numbers before the end of the assigned"
" number of rounds, and your score is higher than your opponent's."
msgstr ""
"You can also win if you close all the numbers before the end of the assigned"
" number of rounds, and your score is higher than your opponent's."

msgctxt "176"
msgid "Have fun and give it your all."
msgstr "Have fun and give it your all."
